Is this the naive implementation, or is this totally wrong?
```
std::vector<double> input(...);
std::vector<double> output(...);
double alpha = 0.5;
auto running_sum = 0;

for (auto i = 0; i < input.size(); i++) {
  running_sum = input[i] + running_sum * (1 - alpha);
  output[i] = running_sum;
}
```
